gr.auth.csd.taskmanager

Class MemoryInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • gr.auth.csd.taskmanager.MemoryInfo

  • public class MemoryInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the information captured from the device on a single day, meaning the internal/external memory that is currently available as well as their total size. Created by Steve Laskaridis on 1/5/2015.
